snippet.title: TOAST CYPHER 2021
snippet.description: An artistic showcase by versatile and talented young Nigerian artists. The toast cypher 2021 is definitely the first of its kind and we look forward to showcasing more dynamic indigenous talents. This cypher was produced by Cozy Media and comprised of 7 artists, Calli-ber tha grime, Victor Alumma, Ayamtu, Uncle B , Cozy lomo, Sules and JaguarAbel. Music production by Cali-ber tha grime. Camera operator, Adedayo Onibanjo.

snippet.title: How to learn data science in 2021 (the minimize effort maximize outcome way)
snippet.description:
